<h1><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358058" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-11-pro-feature-image-1500x999.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="999" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-11-pro-feature-image-1500x999.jpg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-11-pro-feature-image-1500x999-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-11-pro-feature-image-1500x999-768x511.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iphone-11-pro-feature-image-1500x999-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></h1>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293887" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>最新疫情数字</h4>
<p><strong>国内（不含港澳台）已公布数据</strong>：截至 8 月 12 日零时，上海市报告 4 例境外输入性新冠肺炎确诊病例；内蒙古自治区报告新增境外输入确诊病例 1 例。</p>
<p><strong>香港</strong>：截至 11 日零时，新增 33 例确诊病例，1 例为境外输入病例，32 例为本地感染病例。香港累计报告确诊病例 4181 例。</p>
<p><strong>海外</strong>：截至 8 月 12 日 7 时，海外累计确诊病例 20260580 例，累计死亡 736043 例，累计治愈 13413803 例。</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.cs.com.cn/ssgs/gsxw/202008/t20200811_6084336.html">iPhone 供应链公司：没有收到苹果下调 iPhone12 出货指引的通知</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358031" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ere.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ere.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ere-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ere-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ere-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>中证网分别从两家 iPhone 供应链公司以及知情人士得知，目前苹果没有下调 iPhone 12 出货目标指引；此外，一家 iPhone 元器件供应链公司相关人士也向记者表示没有收到苹果下调 iPhone 12 出货目标的通知。</p>
<p>此前，天风证券分析师郭明錤曾分析，如果苹果从全球 App Store 上移除微信，iPhone 年出货量将因此而下修 25%-30%。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/PrZmO7f-sGH787rWsu7tLw">小米发布透明电视，售价 49999 元</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358032" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6f4dac20-dbe0-11ea-9ecf-04827ca8b5a8.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6f4dac20-dbe0-11ea-9ecf-04827ca8b5a8.jpeg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6f4dac20-dbe0-11ea-9ecf-04827ca8b5a8-360x225.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6f4dac20-dbe0-11ea-9ecf-04827ca8b5a8-768x480.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6f4dac20-dbe0-11ea-9ecf-04827ca8b5a8-1024x640.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>昨天，小米发布了全球第一台量产透明电视，屏幕真正实现了全透明观感。小米透明电视的屏幕为 55 英寸 OLED ，厚度为 5.7mm，采用了 MTK 9650 高端芯片，售价 49999 元。</p>
<p>除此以外，小米在昨晚还发布了小米 10 至尊纪念版、Redmi K30 至尊纪念版和智能追踪无线充等多个新硬件，详情可<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/PrZmO7f-sGH787rWsu7tLw">点击这里</a>看爱范儿的完整发布会总结。</p>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/1682207150/JfnJU34Ps?refer_flag=1001030103_">广州试点地上红绿灯，提醒「低头族」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358033" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/street.gif" alt="" width="490" height="270" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/street.gif 490w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/street-360x198.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" /></p>
<p>《南方都市报》消息，由广州市交通运输局牵头，广州交警协助开展的「智慧斑马线项目」在天河北路和林和西路十字路口试点。</p>
<p>这种红绿灯嵌在地上，旨在提醒「低头族」红路灯的改变，每晚 7 点左右开始亮起。</p>
<h4><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293888" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png" alt="" width="1715" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png 1715w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px" /></h4>
<h4><a href="https://newatlas.com/electronics/brick-batteries-store-energy-walls/">砖头也能当电池？</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358034" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/brick.jpg" alt="" width="963" height="642" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/brick.jpg 963w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/brick-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/brick-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 963px) 100vw, 963px" /></p>
<p>New Atlas 消息，圣路易斯华盛顿大学的科学家研发出一种可将砖头转化为电池的解决方案。他们在普通红砖涂上一种导电的聚合物「聚乙撑二氧噻吩（PEDOT）」，这种物质将渗透于砖头的间隙中，让砖头带有储存能量和导电功能。</p>
<p>将「砖头电池」堆叠起来，并加上一层环氧树脂，科学家甚至可建立一面容量更大的「墙电池」。未来，他们希望将这种技术和太阳能等可再生能源组合使用。</p>
