<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/VluaUifDV7ugemacZJY6OA">IDC：Q2 中国平板电脑市场出货量同比增长 17.7%</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358039" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iPad-7-MacBook-Pro-on-table.jpeg" alt="" width="3840" height="1920" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iPad-7-MacBook-Pro-on-table.jpeg 3840w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iPad-7-MacBook-Pro-on-table-360x180.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iPad-7-MacBook-Pro-on-table-768x384.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/iPad-7-MacBook-Pro-on-table-1024x512.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3840px) 100vw, 3840px" /></p>
<p>IDC 新报告指出，2020 年第二季度中国平板电脑市场出货量约 661 万台，同比增长 17.7%，「后疫情」时代，中国平板电脑市场快速恢复。</p>
<p>品牌方面，苹果重返出货量第一，占总量 41.8%；华为位居第二，同比增长 59.5%，同比增幅最高，市场份额占比 37.1%；微软排名第三，同比增长 16%，市场份额为 3.5%。</p>
<h4><a href="https://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2020-08-12/doc-iivhuipn8145830.shtml">爱彼迎计划 8 月递交 IPO，估值降至 180 亿美元</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358040" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/I0nZ3d8bNQe-QYstQGZWnCIq6e20i16EHJLGVxySxlc.jpeg" alt="" width="2500" height="1669" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/I0nZ3d8bNQe-QYstQGZWnCIq6e20i16EHJLGVxySxlc.jpeg 2500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/I0nZ3d8bNQe-QYstQGZWnCIq6e20i16EHJLGVxySxlc-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/I0nZ3d8bNQe-QYstQGZWnCIq6e20i16EHJLGVxySxlc-768x513.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/I0nZ3d8bNQe-QYstQGZWnCIq6e20i16EHJLGVxySxlc-1024x684.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /></p>
<p>新浪科技消息，知情人士透露爱彼迎计划于本月向美国证券交易委员会秘密提交 IPO 上市文件。</p>
<p>爱彼迎原计划更早上市，但因受疫情影响而暂时搁置了 IPO 计划，并裁员 25% 以削减成本。爱彼迎在私募市场上的估值已经下降至 180 亿美元，远低于此前达到的 310 亿美元。</p>
