<h4><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-08-10/covid-19-cases-among-u-s-children-jumped-40-in-late-july?cmpid=BBD081020_BIZ&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_term=200810&amp;utm_campaign=bloombergdaily">七月下旬，美国儿童确诊人数快速跃升</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358042" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/CH1126060.jpg" alt="" width="810" height="494" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/CH1126060.jpg 810w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/CH1126060-360x220.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/CH1126060-768x468.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px" /></p>
<p>《彭博社》消息，据美国儿科学会和儿童医院协会统计，在 7 月 16-30 日间，美国儿童中感染新冠肺炎的人数增加了超过九万人，增长达到 40%。目前，儿童占总确诊病例 8.8%。</p>
<p>部分父母希望可让孩子尽快恢复上学，但也有人担忧如果在 9 月集体恢复上学，容易引起大规模疫情爆发。</p>
